    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS SPICER AUTOMATE-2 - LUBRICATION</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>LUBRICATION</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>To ensure proper lubrication and operating temperatures in this unit, the proper lubricants must be
                used. Correct oil levels must be maintained. Spicer recommends using only lubricants produced by
                reputable, well known suppliers. If you want to use a lubricant not specified below, please contact your
                local truck dealer to determine whether the lubricant is suitable for your purposes.
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
        <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
            <title>RECOMMENDED LUBRICANTS</title>
            <para>Synthetic oil is required with this transmission.</para>
            <table id="t1302201" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
